ActCanadian Commercial Corporation Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for International Trade of CHRISTA C. WESSEL of Oakville, Ontario, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Commercial Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year, in the place of Stephen Sorocky, whose term has expired.
